-- China Encourages Foreign Investment in High-End Manufacturing
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-07-17T01:25:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-17/china-encourages-foreign-investment-in-high-end-manufacturing.html
China  will encoruage foreign
investment into industries including high-end manufacturing,
technology and new energy, National Development and Reform
Commission Chairman Zhang Ping said.  The U.S. and China will start cooperating on infrastructure
construction, Zhang said at the U.S.-China Investment
Cooperation Forum in Beijing.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
